modShortDescription: This mod adds some nice Speedtree's to the 7 Days to Die. Multi-Dim collider issue is on trees too, so you'll need to hit the lower 1x1x1 section of tree.
modDescription:
This mod adds some nice Speedtree’s to the 7 Days to Die. Multi-Dim collider issue is on trees too, so you’ll need to “hit” the lower 1x1x1 section of the [tree](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-trees/), although the movement portion works on the whole collider. Very weird.

[Download](https://gitlab.com/guppycur/guppymods/-/archive/master/guppymods-master.zip?path=Guppycur%27s_Trees)

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/9144-guppycurs-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Guppycur](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/guppycur/)
